This potion is a wonderful restorative, healing damage and curing most ill effects as though by a Heal spell. The flask is light, and only the tightly corked seal suggests there is liquid within.
This tonic is sovereign against venoms, mineral toxins, diseases, and poisons of all sorts.

These magic containers allow you to sell a large number of items to stores, without having to sell each individual item.  The price you receive will be identical the price you would have gotten from selling normally.
